<Base title="SocialProof for Accountants & CPAs — Client Testimonials That Win Referrals | SocialProof" description="Accountants and CPAs: automate client testimonials, build trust with prospects, and grow referrals. SocialProof makes it easy to collect and display social proof.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Accountants & CPAs
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Referrals drive accounting practices — but most prospects still Google you first. SocialProof helps you capture client testimonials automatically and display them exactly where new clients are evaluating you.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why testimonials matter more for accountants</h2>
      <p>Accounting is high-trust. Clients are handing over their financial life. A warm referral is gold — but it only works if the referred prospect can verify you're as good as their friend says. Your website is that verification. Without visible client endorsements, even a referred prospect may ghost you.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof gives you a widget that shows real client feedback — tax prep, bookkeeping, CFO advisory, whatever you specialize in — front and center on your site.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What types of testimonials convert best for CPAs</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Stress reduction:</strong> "They took tax season from a nightmare to a non-event."</li>
        <li><strong>Money saved:</strong> "Found deductions I'd been missing for three years — paid for themselves instantly."</li>
        <li><strong>Responsiveness:</strong> "Always answers the phone during crunch time. Worth every penny."</li>
        <li><strong>Relationship quality:</strong> "Feels like having a CFO on call. They actually understand my business."</li>
        <li><strong>Peace of mind:</strong> "First time I've filed without dreading an audit. Couldn't recommend more."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your practice</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your homepage and services pages in under 10 minutes — no developer needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Send the collection link</strong> to clients after tax season, quarterly closes, or onboarding — one URL, no login required for them.</li>
        <li><strong>Testimonials appear automatically</strong> on your site after a simple one-click approval.</li>
        <li><strong>Rotate and feature</strong> the most relevant testimonials for each service you offer.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The "busy season" problem — solved</h2>
      <p>Accounting firms are buried from January through April. Nobody has time to manually chase testimonials during peak season. SocialProof's automated collection sequences mean you can set up a post-filing email once and testimonials roll in on autopilot every year. Your marketing works even when you're deep in returns.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every accounting specialty</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Individual & family tax preparation</li>
        <li>Small business bookkeeping & tax</li>
        <li>Fractional CFO services</li>
        <li>Nonprofit accounting</li>
        <li>Real estate investor accounting</li>
        <li>Startup & ecommerce accounting</li>
        <li>Payroll & compliance</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background:#f0f9ff;border:1px solid #bae6fd;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#1e40af;">
          "After tax season I sent the SocialProof link to 40 clients. Got 22 testimonials in two weeks. My website went from looking generic to looking like the obvious choice in my city."
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#1e3a8a;">— CPA, boutique tax firm</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Pricing designed for solo and small practices</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget — enough to get started and start converting. Paid plans scale with your firm size and the number of services you want to highlight. No long-term contracts. No per-testimonial fees.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <a href="/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
          Start free — no credit card needed
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;">Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

